## ğŸ› ï¸ What Gets Audited?

### Python
**System-wide:**
- âœ… Installed interpreters (`python`, `python3`, `py`)
- âœ… Global packages with versions
- âœ… Framework detection (Django, Flask, FastAPI, Pyramid)
- âœ… Outdated packages

**Project-specific (with --target):**
- âœ… requirements.txt parsing
- âœ… pyproject.toml detection
- âœ… Pipfile detection
- âœ… Virtual environment (venv/) detection and package listing

### Node.js/npm
**System-wide:**
- âœ… Node.js and npm versions
- âœ… Global packages
- âœ… Framework detection (Express, React, Vue, Angular, Next.js)
- âœ… Outdated global packages

**Project-specific (with --target):**
- âœ… package.json parsing (dependencies, devDependencies, scripts)
- âœ… package-lock.json detection
- âœ… node_modules/ analysis and package count

### Docker
- âœ… Docker version
- âœ… Running/stopped containers
- âœ… Images with sizes
- âœ… Dangling images
- âœ… Large images (>500MB)

### Go
**System-wide:**
- âœ… Go version
- âœ… Module cache location

**Project-specific (with --target):**
- âœ… go.mod parsing (module name, Go version)
- âœ… go.sum detection
- âœ… Module dependency listing

### System
- âœ… Git
- âœ… Docker Compose
- âœ… Kubectl
- âœ… Terraform
- âœ… AWS CLI
- âœ… Azure CLI
- âœ… gcloud
- âœ… Windows installed programs (Windows only)

